name: ipykernel
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "4.5.2" %}

package:
  name: ipykernel
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: ipykernel-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/i/ipykernel/ipykernel-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 5a54f25f0e6c8ee74c362c23f9a95e10e74c6b7f5ef42059c861ff6f26d89462

build:
  number: 0
  script:
    - pip install --no-deps .
    - python -m ipykernel install --prefix $PREFIX  # [not win]
    - python -m ipykernel install --prefix %PREFIX%  # [win]

requirements:
  build:
    - pip
    - python
    - jupyter_client
    - ipython >=4.0
    - tornado >=4.0
  run:
    - python
    - ipython >=4.0
    - traitlets
    - jupyter_client
    - tornado >=4.0

test:
  imports:
    - ipykernel

about:
  home: http://ipython.org
  license: BSD 3-clause
  license_file: COPYING.md
  summary: IPython Kernel for Jupyter

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - jakirkham
    - pelson
    - minrk
    - ocefpaf
